  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">The focus of this repetition is on these sentences:</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Sentence 1 - ひろい　へやですね。= It is a big room.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Sentence 2 - これ　すてきな　えですね。= This is a beautiful painting.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Sentence 3 - それは　あねが　かいた　えです。= My older sister drew the drawing.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Sentence 4 - これは　あねに　もらった　おかしです。= I got these sweets from my older sister.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">How to use this lesson - When the repeat message shows and the video pauses, please repeat the sentence you have just heard. Keep practising until you can repeat perfectly!</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/brq5ud4obr2ovliosd6g\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"D36 L1 R1.mp4 - 00:23\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span></span><br></p></div>",
